description:
A free and lightweight video compression software.

Free Video Compressor is a free and lightweight compression software for video files, it can help you to easily compress video files and save your PC disk space. This software can work with many popular video formats, such as MP4 (MPEG), WMV, FLV, AVI, MOV, MKV, ASF, MPG, RMVB (RM) and more.
